InstruPass1 - To generate CallGraph based metrics
InstruPass2 - To generate per function CFG based metrics

Use passes like -dot-cfg, -dot-callgraph, -dot-dom to generate corresponding dot files which can be viewed and used for testing

To invoke passes:
opt -load {Path to LLVM Objects folder}/Release+Asserts/lib/LLVMCustom.so -instruPass1 -stats < test.bc
opt -load {Path to LLVM Objects folder}/Release+Asserts/lib/LLVMCustom.so -instruPass2 -stats < test.bc
opt -load {Path to LLVM Objects folder}/Release+Asserts/lib/LLVMCustom.so -deadCodeRemoval < test.bc




To view dot files:
dot -Tps {dot file name} | gv - &



Note:
For debugging, you can use;
errs() << "Debug Statement;
instead of the usual
cout << "Debug Statement;

